    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "### Problem\n\nI find it's convenient to set case insensitive for searching and case sensitive for replacing.  However, current version of neovim doesn't seem to support this feature.\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nCan you add an option such that we can set  case sensitivity seperately for searching and replacing?",
