            "author_association": "NONE",
            "body": "Maybe something like this would work?\r\n```lua\r\nvim.api.nvim_create_autocmd(\"CmdlineEnter\", {\r\n   pattern = { \"/\", '?' },\r\n   callback = function()\r\n      vim.o.ignorecase = true\r\n   end\r\n})\r\n\r\nvim.api.nvim_create_autocmd(\"CmdlineEnter\", {\r\n   pattern = ':',\r\n   callback = function()\r\n      vim.o.ignorecase = false\r\n   end\r\n})\r\n```",
